0.1.name: wordpress/remove-default-canonical-links
0.1.description:
Quick plugin to disable all default WordPress canonical links on your pages. Can be used if you're generating canonical links through other means, to avoid duplicate link entries.

For more information on canonical links, see Matt Cutt's blog entry
